content:
For awareness: we are moving the vote to launch WASI Preview 2 from this week's (1/11) meeting to the 1/25 meeting: https://github.com/WebAssembly/meetings/pull/1460

WASI: Reschedule vote for WASI Preview 2 launch from 1/11 to 1/25 by pchickey 路 Pull Request #1460 路 WebAssembly/meetings
On 1/11, @gbedford will give an update on the JCO implementation progress, which is close to completion. On 1/25, we will hear about the conclusion of the JCO implementation work, and hold the vote...
We will also delay the release of Wasmtime 17 to 1/26 or 27, so that we can increment the wit versions to 0.2.0 (just dropping the -rc part of the version numbers)
